cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about natural language generation using the Transformer model.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to improve the generation quality of the Transformer model.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with natural language generation, which is a subfield of AI.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the Transformer model is a neural network architecture.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the Transformer model has also been applied to image-related tasks.
